{"tid":1650370,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【唔好制裁我】葉劉促美國會勿通過《人權法案》","createTime":"2019-10-13T02:31:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T18:29:39.000Z","uid":184679,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"af37d174cb2242a960689b10565b4e3a0fda1bb4","tid":1650370,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T02:31:39.000Z","msg":"美國國會本周三將審議《香港人權及民主法案》，新民黨主席葉劉淑儀、自由黨黨魁鍾國斌、公民黨黨魁楊岳橋及法律界郭榮鏗等六名立法會議員，前日與訪港的美國參議院五名高級議員助理會面。<br />\n<br />\n葉劉淑儀在社交網站發文，提到會面時對方話很多美國人並不了解「一國兩制」及香港實際狀況，今次到訪令他們感受到香港是一個非常獨特的地方，很高興可以親身了解香港真正面貌。葉劉淑儀又指，她在會面上表明反對美國國會要通過《法案》，呼籲國會議員投反對票，一如以往維持香港的獨特地位。<br />\n<br />\n楊岳橋則表示，他們在會面上談到本港過去數個月屢見示威的成因、為何港人堅持五大訴求，以及成立獨立調查委員會、處理警暴問題和落實雙普選等的重要性。他和郭榮鏗席間都表態支持美國國會通過《法案》，他並向對方解釋現時本港所享的「一國兩制」，屬走數版的「一國兩制」。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1611681/</code></pre>"},{"pid":"7b91fd6b9778ee4a05852631d8ee898db81be445","tid":1650370,"uid":130626,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T02:33:23.000Z","msg":"姐姐真係好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d6e7d8129e4ab3a2dc404bfcdf4651c15b63248","tid":1650370,"uid":297334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T02:33:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gZJb5kM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgZJb5kM.png&h=c27e3929&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WJcsDFN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWJcsDFN.png&h=d3f5ad94&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6YijuNt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6YijuNt.png&h=dc821f5b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"538ec1d732bd72eb947a9e0edbbff5f60b6490ee","tid":1650370,"uid":322230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T02:33: